{"tid":789094,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"土司工坊真心求撚其","createTime":"2018-08-22T03:50:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-22T22:29:26.000Z","uid":105083,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"affa5187e857d29fac04e19a9d6a3938bc58532f","tid":789094,"uid":105083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T03:50:16.000Z","msg":"叫個菠蘿油餐加半熟蛋熱啡<br />\n<br />\n個菠蘿包面頭淋撚曬<br />\n濕笠笠完全唔脆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個色咬落去一啲都唔鬆化<br />\n乾到閪咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n隻半熟蛋即場開殼嘅<br />\n個收銀對手收完現金<br />\n兩隻手指公直隊入去隻蛋度<br />\n再擘開個殼<br />\n仲要隻蛋俾佢隻手指公隊撚爛左<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唯一可取係杯熱啡<br />\n叫做即拉<br />\n不過都係做下樣拉一兩下<br />\n味道正常<br />\n是撚但<br />\n<br />\n屌埋單$37<br />\n茶餐嚟講唔係話貴<br />\n但係唔知自己食左乜撚嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06a18b89e4306339789b0f59d2709cc6b7dc78fc","tid":789094,"uid":195169,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T04:06:44.000Z","msg":"屌以前好撚好食<br />\n2,3年前已經唔同曬, 越嚟越垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7d0b37e6bcbb3fb82ecc9619fa8df97551668ba","tid":789094,"uid":176063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T04:13:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e6606360908895d49cc3da9688c67a00adb2cb81","tid":789094,"uid":31186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T04:55:25.000Z","msg":"食過一次之後狗也不屌<br />\n難食到痴線"},{"pid":"bceb3952